quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  62,9,"O You who have chosen to be graced with belief! When the prayer is announced on the Day of the Congregation, hasten to the remembrance of Allah and leave your commerce. That is for your own good if you use your knowledge to understand"
  62,10,"And when the prayer is ended, disperse freely in the land and seek of Allah's Bounty. And remember Allah often so that you may prosper"
  62,11,"Yet when they see some bargain or entertainment, they rush to it, and leave you standing. Say, \"That which is with Allah is better than all entertainment and all bargain. And Allah is the Best of providers"